<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.2.8">
<l>mēvu tuṉpa viṉaikaḷai viṭuttumilē</l>
<l>ṉōvuta liṉṟi yuṉkaḻal vaṇaṅkiṟṟilēṉ</l>
<l>pāvutol cīrkkaṇ ṇāveṉ parañcuṭarē</l>
<l>kūvukiṉṟēṉ kāṇpā ṉeṅkeytak kūvuvaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I am without getting rid of the miserable karmas that are attached [to me]</l>
<l>and I am without bowing to your anklet[ed feet] without stopping.</l>
<l>O Kṛṣṇa of pervasive ancient excellence, my highest glow,</l>
<l>I call. How shall I call to reach [you] in order so see you?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
